description: The investment seeks to provide total return. In pursuing the fund's investment objective, the fund will invest in ETFs that primarily invest in fixed income securities, real estate investment trusts ("REITs"), master limited partnerships ("MLPs"), dividend paying equity stocks including utility stocks, put options, U.S. treasuries and exchange-traded notes ("ETNs"). Fixed Income ETFs will include those that invest in domestic and foreign fixed income securities of any credit rating maturity and duration.
name: Trend Aggregation Conservative ETF
